{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_69","type":"agent_message","text":"I found two viable ways the repo already uses for native-test-only issues: pass extra native-image `buildArgs`, or add JVM args/system properties in the test build. For JAXB, the cleaner first attempt is to push the existing `ClassTailor.noOptimize=true` toggle into the test build itself so the optimizer path never reaches `Injector` during image analysis. If that still doesn’t take, the fallback is a native-test-only `--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED`, which the repo already uses in other tests."}}
